1.00	40-Year_Old_Virgin	The 40-Year-Old Virgin	The 40-Year-Old Virgin is a 2005 American buddy comedy film about a middle-aged man's journey to finally have sex. The film was written and directed by Judd Apatow and co-written by its lead star, Steve Carell, though the film itself features a great deal of improvised dialogue. The film received its general North American theatrical release on August 19, 2005 and was released on region 1 DVD on December 13, 2005.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/4/43/40-Year-OldVirginMoviePoster.jpg/220px-40-Year-OldVirginMoviePoster.jpg
